      "content": "but doctors and counselors... they just don't get it. they talk about \"management\" and \"coping\" but the pain stays the same. it's like they're asking me to just learn to love a fire that's burning me alive. sometimes i feel like the world is just moving on around me and i'm just trapped in this body, stuck in this constant loop of agony. it doesn't feel like a \"challenge\" to overcome anymore. it just feels like a dead end.",
