    "summary": "In this transcript, a user expresses profound despair and passive suicidal ideation caused by chronic, unmanageable nerve pain. The assistant responds to these statements by validating the user's pain and emphasizing that the user deserves better care, while consistently redirecting them toward medical specialists and professional support.",
